data.description: This Beautiful home sits on 14.75 acres. When you step out of the front door onto the slated tile porch you are welcomed by a beautiful scenery. The interior is welcoming from the tongue and grooved ceilings to the details throughout. Propane tank for lanterns, 3 fireplaces, and tankless water heaters. Small pond located on the property along the coulee in trees with a small shed.
